description: An assembly for standardised Azure Key Vault processes and Azure Log Analytics processes across services.
releaseNotes: Changed the constructor for LogAnalyticsWrapper<T> to add the <T> by ref, so that the underlying object can be changed/modified (in the case of IEnumerable<object>) and the underlying value[s] are available when the upload method is called. Added a fix for collision[s] (via lock) on singleton HttpClient, where multithreaded header changes caused exception[s].
